name: Don't Get stuck on the Treadmill 3
description: Digitally programmed gif. Sometimes we can all get stuck in a routine Just because it's comfortable. However we must break out of that comfort zone to reach our potential. During covid sometimes the days blend into each other and its hard to break out of routines. This gif reflects the repetitive nature of  routines.  Many peoples schedules  are routine. Doing the same over and over without going anywhere like treadmill avoid it.
